messages.content: You are tasked with creating a structured output from the provided user message.

Files containing the implementation of App\Http\Controllers\PostLikeController::store

- app/Http/Controllers/PostLikeController.php

Explanation
- The route in routes/auth.php maps POST /posts/{post}/likes to App\Http\Controllers\PostLikeController::store.  
- The file app/Http/Controllers/PostLikeController.php (namespace App\Http\Controllers) defines the store(Post $post) method that performs $post->like() and returns a MultiplePendingTurboStreamResponse (Turbo Stream responses updating the like button and likes count).
- There is another class named PostLikeController at app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/PostLikeController.php, but its namespace is App\Http\Controllers\Api\V1 so it is a different controller and not the one referenced by routes/auth.php.
